		{
			dependencies: []
			description: [
				"Welcome to Cobblemon! Start your journey by choosing a §eStarter Pok\u00e9mon§r."
				""
				"§7How to get your starter:§r Find a §ePok\u00e9 Starter§r NPC in your starting area, or use the §e/pokespawn§r command if enabled. Your starter is yours from the very beginning \u2014 no catching required."
				""
				"Your starter begins at §eLvl 5§r and comes with a set of starting moves. Take it into battle to gain XP and level up!"
				""
				"§7Tip:§r Hold §eSneak + Right-click§r on your Pok\u00e9mon while it's out to see its stats, moves, and IVs at any time."
			]
			icon: "cobblemon:poke_ball"
			id: "3000"
			rewards: [
