		{
			dependencies: ["3000"]
			description: [
				"§eApricorns§r are coloured fruit that grow on Apricorn trees \u2014 the raw ingredient for all Pok\u00e9 Balls."
				""
				"§7Where to find them:§r Apricorn trees spawn naturally across the overworld. Look for small, distinctive trees with coloured fruit. Break the fruit block (not the tree) to harvest the apricorn."
				""
				"§7Farming:§r You can plant §eApricorn Seeds§r to grow your own trees. Break a ripe apricorn to get the seed and the fruit. A small apricorn farm ensures a steady Pok\u00e9 Ball supply well into late game."
				""
				"§7Ball ingredients:§r Each apricorn colour makes a different Pok\u00e9 Ball type. Check JEI or the Pok\u00e9dex for the full recipe list."
			]
			id: "3010"
			rewards: [
				{
					count: 4
