				}
			]
			title: "Harvest an Apricorn"
			subtitle: "Find an Apricorn tree and harvest your first Apricorn \u2014 the foundation of every Pok\u00e9 Ball type."
			x: 2.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["3010"]
			description: [
				"Your first §ePok\u00e9 Ball§r! Catching wild Pok\u00e9mon is the core Cobblemon loop."
				""
				"§7How to catch:§r Find a wild Pok\u00e9mon, approach it to start battle, weaken it with your starter (lower HP = higher catch rate), then select §eBag§r \u2192 §ePok\u00e9 Ball§r and throw."
				""
				"§7Ball recipe:§r §7Apricorn§r \u2192 smelt \u2192 §7Disc§r + craft §7Button§r + §7Ball Base§r \u2192 crafting table \u2192 §ePok\u00e9 Ball§r. Full recipe in JEI."
				""
				"§7Status helps:§r Putting a Pok\u00e9mon to §eSleep§r or §eParalysing§r it doubles the catch rate. Carry some Potions and a Pok\u00e9mon that knows Sleep Powder or Thunder Wave for tough catches."
			]
			id: "3011"
			rewards: [
				{
					count: 5
