		{
			dependencies: ["3011"]
			description: [
				"Win your §efirst Pok\u00e9mon battle§r! Battle wild Pok\u00e9mon and trainer NPCs to earn XP and level up."
				""
				"§7Battle basics:§r Each turn you choose a move, use an item from your bag, switch Pok\u00e9mon, or attempt to run. Moves have types \u2014 match your type to the opponent's weakness for 2\u00d7 damage."
				""
				"§7Levels:§r Pok\u00e9mon level up through battle XP. Higher levels unlock new moves and trigger evolutions. Check your Pok\u00e9mon's summary screen to see when it learns the next move."
				""
				"§7Tip:§r If your starter is struggling, catch a few different Pok\u00e9mon to build a balanced team covering multiple types."
			]
			id: "3012"
			rewards: [
