				""
				"§7Where to look:§r Different biomes spawn different Pok\u00e9mon. Explore forests, caves, deserts, oceans, and mountains to diversify your party."
				""
				"§7Once you're full:§r You'll need a §ePC§r to store extras. Pok\u00e9mon in the PC don't gain XP, so consider rotating your team regularly."
