				"§7Rideable Pok\u00e9mon:§r Large ground types (Mudsdale, Rhyhorn), fast Pok\u00e9mon (Rapidash, Arcanine), and some water types can all be ridden."
				""
				"§7How:§r With the Pok\u00e9mon in your party and out of its ball, press §eRight-click§r on it to mount. Use movement keys to steer."
				""
				"§7Mount upgrades:§r Feed your mount §eAprijuice§r (brewed from Apricorns in a Campfire Pot) to improve its §eSpeed§r, §eStamina§r, and §eJump§r stats. A maxed-out mount is substantially faster than a horse."
