				"Used the §ePasture§r block! The Pasture lets your Pok\u00e9mon roam freely in a defined outdoor area \u2014 great for passive display and §ebreeding§r."
				""
				"§7Pasture + Breeding:§r Place two compatible Pok\u00e9mon of opposite genders in the same Pasture. They will eventually produce an §eEgg§r. The egg hatches as you walk around with it in your party."
				""
				"§7Why breed?§r IV inheritance \u2014 bred offspring can inherit up to 3 perfect IVs from parents. Use §eEver Stone§r to pass down a Nature. §ePower Items§r guarantee specific IV inheritance."
